Class PAMSFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pcc.pams.PAMSFrame

  • class PAMSFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    The simulation frame, on which everything is drawn.

    This is mostly a placeholder file; to generate its methods, it must be built in conjunction with IntelliJ's form editor.
